<p><strong>Brisbane, {{ date | readableDate }}</strong>
<p>OneQode & Oracle are proud to announce our partnership for high-performance infrastructure across Asia-Pacific and beyond</p>
<div class="callout col-xs-12 p-2 my-2" id="key-facts">
	<h2>Key facts</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>OneQode and Oracle are partnering to develop integrated cloud solutions for Asia-Pacific and beyond.</li>
		<li>Oracle will be able to integrate APAC Central into its broader product offering, allowing for region wide approaches.</li>
		<li>OneQode’s high-performance latency optimised cloud compute along with Oracle&#39;s enterprise cloud will set a new high standard for latency and connectivity across APAC.</li>
	</ul>
</div>
<p>The partnership is poised to set a new regional standard for cloud computing across the region. </p>
